1. My grandfather has many pens. His pens are red. He likes the pens.
2. I like tea. My mother likes sweet tea.
3. I have two computers. The computers are not new. The computers are old.
4. This is a pen. This pen is green. It is not red.
5. This is butter. The butter is yellow. The butter is not white.
6. We have a cat. It is three. I like the cat. He is clever.
7. My sister has three cats. She likes her cats. The cats are beautiful.
8. He has ice cream. The ice cream is sweet.
9. We have many friends. They are students.
10. I have a brother and a sister. My brother is a pupil, but my sister is a student.
They have many friends. The friends are good boys.
